---
// FirstDip — "For your first time" editorial section
// V1 design, linen card, bordered steps
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="first-dip">
    <div class="first-dip-content">
      <div class="first-dip-eyebrow">iv. · For your first time</div>
      <h3>Your first <em>dip.</em></h3>
      <p class="first-dip-intro">A sound bath isn't a workout, a class, or a performance. You lie down. You close your eyes. Vibrations from bowls, gongs, and voice wash over you for an hour. Most people fall asleep at least a little — that's the point.</p>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">i</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <strong>Arrive ten minutes early.</strong>
            <span>Most spaces lock the door once the session begins. Bring socks, a water bottle, an open mind.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">ii</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <strong>Lie down. That's it.</strong>
            <span>Mats and blankets are provided. You won't be asked to move, chant, or do anything. Just breathe.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">iii</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <strong>Surface slowly afterward.</strong>
            <span>Don't rush back into the day. Walk home. Drink water. Take a note if something rose up.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/guide/first-time" class="first-dip-cta">Read the full guide</a>
    </div>

    <div class="first-dip-visual">
      <img
        src="https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/sarah-barnard-sensory-wellness-room-2-65c4f0a2e2b5f.jpg"
        alt="A warm sound bath room with natural light"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div class="first-dip-caption">A room in Tribeca, photographed at 4:30 PM.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .first-dip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    background: var(--linen);
    padding: 88px 80px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .first-dip-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--clay);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .first-dip h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 56px;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144;
  }
  .first-dip h3 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--clay); }
  .first-dip-intro {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 72;
  }

  .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 52px 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 22px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .step:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 30px;
    color: var(--clay);
    line-height: 1;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 72;
  }
  .step-body strong {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 72;
  }
  .step-body span {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-mid);
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 72;
  }

  .first-dip-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bone);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .first-dip-cta::after { content: "→"; }
  .first-dip-cta:hover { background: var(--clay); }

  .first-dip-visual {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .first-dip-visual img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .first-dip-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px; left: 22px; right: 22px;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--bone);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 72;
  }
  .first-dip-caption::before {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    width: 28px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--bone);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .first-dip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 56px 36px; gap: 48px; }
  }
</style>
